  "title": "Tapping for worthy of millions",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute tapping script for removing the sense that very large wealth belongs to someone else.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 24 of the MONEY program. The script works with the specific belief that millions are for a different type of person, and gradually moves that ceiling.",
