  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 24 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Feel worthy of millions.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
