      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 24 of the MONEY program. The session targets a specific pattern: the word \"millions\" doesn't feel like a number, it feels like a door you're not meant to open. The script names that reaction, works through the round with it, and ends with millions as an ordinary expectation.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how EFT tapping works",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " first.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "The practice",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
